                                Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  This is primarily a recode of the German blu ray release with the English
soundtrack, but with three changes:
 First, was to substitute the first 15 seconds of German printing with
upconverted video (in English) from the R1 DVD. The German release translates,
IMHO, quite differently than the English release, changes the setting for this
great flick.
 The second change was to address the issue of AV sync that the English
soundtrack suffers from, on this BD release. The sync is off slightly, still,
on a couple of scenes, but for most of the movie, it is fine.
 Lastly, I recoded the frame rate to 24000/1001 fps.

  This torrent also includes a couple of songs from the movie that were not
released on the official soundtrack:
 Freakpower - Song #6
 David Holmes - No Man's Land
